Job Details
Senior Cost & Budget Analyst – Natural Energy Industry
Responsibilities
Management and reporting of financial aspects of the cost centre budgets
Payment of 3rdparty invoices
Supervision of preparation of operations business plans
Management and resolution of financial disputes
Essential Skills & Experience Required
8 - 10 years’ experience of preparing revenue analysis and financial reports
Preparation of revenue and manpower budgets, CAPEX and OPEX
Previous experience of the UAE oil & gas industry is an advantage
Experience of an ERP system is essential
Education
Bachelors Degree in Accounting or Finance
Candidate Profile
Aged between 30 – 40 years
Living in the UAE
Fluency in English is essential
To apply – please visit www.plumjobs.co and apply online
Telephone Number - +971 552 167567
Only candidates with relevant experience will be contacted within 2 days of their application
You can connect with us on LinkedIn and follow the Plum Jobs company page or follow us on Twitter and like us on Facebook
